ion for indications unsupported by the current evidence. Given these elements, further research is needed, yet increased caution is recommended when prescribing opioid drugs.</AbstractText>\n            </Abstract>\n            <AuthorList CompleteYN="Y">\n                <Author ValidYN="Y">\n                    <LastName>Ruchat</LastName>\n                    <ForeName>David</ForeName>\n                    <Initials>D</Initials>\n                    <AffiliationInfo>\n                        <Affiliation>Facult\xc3\xa9 de Biologie et M\xc3\xa9decine, Universit\xc3\xa9 de Lausanne UNIL, 1015 Lausanne.</Affiliation>\n                    </AffiliationInfo>\n                </Author>\n                <Author ValidYN="Y">\n                    <LastName>Suter</LastName>\n                    <ForeName>Marc R</ForeName>\n                    <Initials>MR</Initials>\n                    <AffiliationInfo>\n                        <Affiliation>Centre d\'antalgie, Service d\'anesth\xc3\xa9siologie, CHUV, 1011 Lausanne.</Affiliation>\n                    </AffiliationInfo>\n                </Author>\n                <Author ValidYN="Y">\n                    <LastName>Rodondi</LastName>\n                    <ForeName>Pierre-Yves</ForeName>\n                    <Initials>PY</Initials>\n                    <AffiliationInfo>\n                        <Affiliation>Institut fribourgeois de m\xc3\xa9decine de famille, Universit\xc3\xa9 de Fribourg, Rue de Rome 2, 1700 Fribourg.</Affiliation>\n                    </AffiliationInfo>\n                </Author>\n                <Author ValidYN="Y">\n                    <LastName>Berna</LastName>\n                    <ForeName>Chantal</ForeName>\n                    <Initials>C</Initials>\n                    <AffiliationInfo>\n                        <Affiliation>Centre d\'antalgie, Service d\'anesth\xc3\xa9siologie, CHUV, 1011 Lausanne.</Affiliation>\n                    </AffiliationInfo>\n                </Author>\n            </AuthorL